      "subject": "Chemistry",
      "section": "A",
      "questionType": "MCQ",
      "questionText": "The increasing order of the reactivity of the following halides for the S<sub>N</sub>1 reaction is :<br><br>\n<img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/1l7yn9eb0/00fcde9b-e5e4-4493-8e86-5e314ce5e807/befe6ec0-3288-11ed-8893-19b23ee4c66d/file-1l7yn9eb1.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/1l7yn9eb0/00fcde9b-e5e4-4493-8e86-5e314ce5e807/befe6ec0-3288-11ed-8893-19b23ee4c66d/file-1l7yn9eb1.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0px auto;max-height:40vh\" alt=\"JEE Main 2017 (Offline) Chemistry - Haloalkanes and Haloarenes Question 170 English\">",
