      "section": "A",
      "questionType": "MCQ",
      "questionText": "<p>The correct order of reactivity of following haloarenes towards nucleophilic substitution with aqueous $$\\mathrm{NaOH}$$ is :</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/1lgzolc56/26d8aeec-3864-4c15-9ad2-3bca7495b1b7/af38e1a0-e548-11ed-b775-8921c6ad38e2/file-1lgzolc57.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/1lgzolc56/26d8aeec-3864-4c15-9ad2-3bca7495b1b7/af38e1a0-e548-11ed-b775-8921c6ad38e2/file-1lgzolc57.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width: 100%;height: auto;display: block;margin: 0 auto;max-height: 80vh\" alt=\"JEE Main 2023 (Online) 8th April Evening Shift Chemistry - Haloalkanes and Haloarenes Question 65 English\"></p>\n<p>Choose the correct answer from the options given below:</p>",
